己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"a26b3f69a48d893d375d7f135667d689ae5cd0ed","tid":1877843,"uid":162539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"燕南天"},{"pid":"c2715178b1439f5a3ab3def96190a1c7ef2d10a2","tid":1877843,"uid":54387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:49:53.000Z","msg":"切啫啫啦梗係"},{"pid":"47599e3fd3ba211952a0ffbee210b440e3ca1a68","tid":1877843,"uid":170365,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T10:57:02.000Z","msg":"肌肉梗係有用啦<br />\n類似金剛不壞呢啲都係要靠肌肉硬度同密度去做防禦<br />\n肌肉量大啲 啲外功都威力大啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：武林高手"},{"pid":"0d32c4c1957120d5f1d8ddc0424477b77ab72d18","tid":1877843,"uid":82398,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T11:08:43.000Z","msg":"毒撚幻想既世界"},{"pid":"0dc50ccf29551133a99b2fde789a1287a11e57a0","tid":1877843,"uid":76753,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a7ab69d26cd6edc868f7e2fbb13370c306e0a481","tid":1877843,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfcc0da5bffc15cffe9d51c1d734c34c8e03d24e","tid":1877843,"uid":345502,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"925a7b9df58b87563e27172ffc4924451593cc68","tid":1877843,"uid":51346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T08:54:22.000Z","msg":"硬食拳掌用內功抵銷 <br />\n攻擊力又係睇內功<br />\n<br />\n肌肉好似無咩用<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T09:41:17.00